reater Philadelphia area.Aside from the editor, the contributors are Charles Cashdollar, Marie Conn, William W. Cutler III, Deborah Mathias Gough, Ann Greene, Sheldon Hackney, Emma J. Lapsansky-Werner, William Pencak, and Thomas F. Rzeznik.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mai 2021) 7aRELIGION / Christian Church / History.2bisacsh1 aCashdollar, Charles D., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aConn, Marie, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aContosta, David R., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aContosta, David R., eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aCutler, William W., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGough, Deborah Mathias, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGreene, Ann Norton, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHackney, Sheldon, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLapsansky-Werner, Emma Jones, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPencak, William, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRzeznik, Thomas F., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertPenn State University Press Complete eBook-Package Pre-2014z978311074526940uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780271072326423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9780271072326.jpg  a978-3-11-074526-9  Penn State University Press Complete eBook-Package Pre-2014b2014  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK